ADDITIONAL INFORMATION:

Quasar is a high-level compositional framework for SuperCollider.

SuperCollider is also licensed under GPL-3.0.
See: https://github.com/supercollider/supercollider

This project builds upon decades of research in computer music,
music theory, and algorithmic composition. We are grateful to:
- SuperCollider community (James McCartney et al.)
- IRCAM (OpenMusic)
- CCRMA, MIT Media Lab
- Music theory and algorithmic composition research communities

For questions about licensing, please open an issue on GitHub.
